These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, fantasy, zombie, comedy
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, nigerian, german, dutch
1. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the german##1
2. the dutch is on the far left##1
3. the german is between the nigerian and the person watching fantasy movies##2
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching romance movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy         | fantasy   | zombie | romance       |
| Nationality      | dutch | italian | german   | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
City: hannover, venice, miami, liverpool
4 different pets are kept: frog, cat, hedgehog, chinchilla
1. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person traveling to miami and the owner of the cat##2
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| City         | venice | hannover | miami | liverpool |
| Pet   | cat    | chinchilla   | frog | hedgehog       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, handball, soccer, skateboarding
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, mystery, action
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching epic movies and the person who's sport is handball##2
3. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Sport          | skateboarding    | swimming | handball   | soccer  |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | mystery   | action | adventure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, russian, indonesian, brazilian
City: london, san-francisco, paris, berlin
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is the russian##1
2. the dutch is between the person traveling to london and the brazilian##2
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1
4. the dutch is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Nationality     | brazilian   | dutch    | indonesian       | russian   |
| City   | paris | berlin | london | san-francisco |

