.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, marigold, tulip, orchid
City: edinburgh, hamburg, berlin, san-francisco
1. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far right##1
4. the person who growsorchid is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person traveling to hamburg##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Flower   | aconite        | tulip | orchid  | marigold |
| City      | berlin | hamburg  | san-francisco | edinburgh    |

