.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, orchid, amaryllis, aconite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, scientific, martial-arts, mystery
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person who growsaconite is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1
4. the person who growsorchid is the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person who growstulip and the person who growsorchid##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Flower   | orchid     | amaryllis           | tulip | aconite  |
| Movie-Genre         | time-travel | mystery | scientific   | martial-arts |

