.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, hiking, filmmaking, singing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, april, november, may
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby   | singing   | hiking | magic-tricks | filmmaking      |
| Birthday     | november | january    | april  | may |

