.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, october, july, january
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, swisher, bluemaster, ritmeester
1. the blend-smoker is the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the swisher-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in july and the bluemaster-smoker##2
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
4. the blend-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Birthday       | march | january | july     | october   |
| Cigar   | bluemaster   | swisher     | ritmeester | blend |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
4 different games are played: bridge, domino, mah-jongg, scrabble
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, alhambra, blend, swisher
1. the person playing mah-jongg is between the dunhill-smoker and the person playing bridge##2
2. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the left of the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Game         | domino | mah-jongg | bridge | scrabble |
| Cigar   | dunhill         | swisher       | alhambra    | blend         |

