.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, disaster, sports
House: futuristic, modern, ranch-style, cape-cod
1. the modern house is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
4. the ranch-style house is on the right of the modern house##1
5. the modern house is between the person watching documentary movies and the cape-cod house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre    | sports   | disaster      | documentary   | animation  |
| House   | cape-cod | modern | ranch-style | futuristic |

