.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, scooter, tram, taxi
City: berlin, hamburg, venice, rome
1. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person driving the scooter is between the person driving the taxi and the person driving the skateboard##2
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
4. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Transport          | skateboard     | scooter | taxi   | tram        |
| City   | berlin | venice   | hamburg | rome |

