The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, musician, project-manager, photographer
1. the project-manager is the russian##1
2. the musician is on the left of the photographer##1
3. the lawyer is the turkish##1
4. the spanish is the musician##1
5. the lawyer is on the right of the japanese##1
6. the musician is between the russian and the japanese##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Nationality         | russian | spanish | japanese | turkish |
| Job   | project-manager          | musician     | photographer  | lawyer     |

