.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-15::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, ebony, coral, orange
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, june, september, october
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
2. the person who likes orange is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who likes turquise##2
3. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |      4       |
| Color         | turquise      | orange | ebony  | coral |
| Birthday   | june | september  | october | march    |

