.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, may, march, july
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, azure, black, aquamarine
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who likes black##1
3. the person who likes azure is between the person who likes coral and the person who's birthday is in may##2
4. the person who likes aquamarine is the person who likes aquamarine##1
5. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
