.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-18::.
City: berlin, hamburg, liverpool, boston
4 different games are played: snooker, chess, bridge, canasta
1. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person playing snooker and the person traveling to liverpool##2
4. the person traveling to boston is the person playing snooker##1
5. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| City       | boston | hamburg | liverpool | berlin |
| Game   | snooker    | chess  | canasta    | bridge       |

