City: hamburg, liverpool, london, hannover
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person traveling to hamburg##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | fishing   | camping   | photography | card-games |
| City         | hamburg | liverpool | hannover     | london    |

