.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, cabbage, strawberry, zucchini
4 different games are played: canasta, bridge, whist, backgammon
1. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
2. the person eating pineapple is between the person playing canasta and the person eating zucchini##2
3. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person eating cabbage is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food   | strawberry    | zucchini     | pineapple | cabbage |
| Game     | bridge | backgammon | whist       | canasta     |

 